<div style="font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 10px; background-color: #f8f9fa;">
    <h2 style="color: #6f42c1; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">ESPRIT BANK SECURITY</h2>
    <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 2px solid #6f42c1; width: 50px; margin: 0 auto 30px;">
    
    <p>Hello <strong>{{ userName }}</strong>,</p>
    <p>To access your Esprit Banking account, please enter the following 6-digit one-time password (OTP):</p>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 40px 0;">
        <span style="background-color: #fff; color: #1a202e; padding: 15px 30px; border: 2px solid #6f42c1; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0.5rem; display: inline-block; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
            {{ otpCode }}
        </span>
    </div>
    
    <p style="color: #666; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 30px;">This code will expire in <strong>5 minutes</strong>. If you did not request this code, please contact our security team immediately.</p>
    
    <table style="width: 100%; background-color: #fff; border-radius: 8px; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 30px;">
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 20px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #dee2e6;">
                <p style="margin: 0; color: #999; font-size: 12px;">© 2026 Esprit Banking Secure Node. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0 0; color: #999; font-size: 11px;">This is an automated system-generated message. Please do not reply.</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>
